</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-67_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The CQC oversees approximately 31,000 health and social care organisations across England, including private and public sector providers. Statistics reveal that organisations adhering to CQC standards meet legal requirements and achieve higher patient satisfaction and safety outcomes. The importance of understanding and implementing these standards cannot be overstated, as they directly impact the care received by millions of individuals.
