</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:13px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-73_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-74_ pf-text-1"><strong>CQC compliance</strong> - Adherence to the standards and regulations set forth by the Care Quality Commission, which assesses health and social care services against key safety, effectiveness, care, responsiveness, and leadership criteria.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-76_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regulated activities</strong> - Specific care and treatment services that require CQC registration under the Health and Social Care Act 2008.
