<h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-88_ pf-heading-1-h3">Relevant legislation and regulations
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-90_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The regulatory framework surrounding CQC compliance primarily stems from the following:
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:13px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-92_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-93_ pf-text-1">The Health and Social Care Act 2008
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-95_ pf-text-1">The Care Act 2014
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-97_ pf-text-1">The CQC (Registration) Regulations 2009</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-99_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">These documents outline the standards and responsibilities of providers in ensuring high-quality and safe care.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-101_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-102_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-103_ pf-heading-1-h3">Best practices
